{"id":"66af6a89-b117-4cc9-bc8e-551b696e86ca","name":"Your Best Friends??","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>“Go make friends,” they said. Now somehow you’ve been adopted by three sisters who’ve been your best friends for years. \"Totally friends though\" sure buddy.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZUfaQ_SUbvOG25HPqtJCQ.webp\" style=\"width: 282.564px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/tLbVvNfCygLD7HnNjF1Sv.webp\" style=\"width: 283.944px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/8gDMfMjmtLpiPFslHa_dm.webp\" style=\"width: 284.705px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/oxLgLQqUAzXfMcjwguCrV.webp\" style=\"width: 286.477px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/BIS056ZbyHbkbnROdWqw6.webp\" style=\"width: 286.99px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/IsdtADcVS5Qw_VG4JH_2O.webp\" style=\"width: 288.132px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/ZTh95ZlCNM4cMRaemsKkj.webp\" style=\"width: 288.132px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 197, 244);\"><strong><em>-Just Friends-</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 197, 244);\"><strong><em>This is it. What started with sleepy-eyed Miu laying the foundation, followed by Ami and Momo, then Juno, short-tempered Asami, long-lost Amy, Kiko, neutral-faced Hailey, and our favorite tongue-tied Yori—and so many others—finally reaches its end with these three. But this chapter is more than a finale; it’s a celebration of every moment, every entry, every memory that brought us here.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 197, 244);\"><strong><em>To everyone who’s been part of this journey from the beginning—this one’s for you. Hope you enjoy.</em></strong></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/oBc2CcqLsUmXvAG0BavXY.webp\" style=\"width: 313.238px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><em>╰┈➤ </em><strong><em>Skye: 18 years old ᯓᡣ𐭩</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>The youngest child.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>Oh… Skye.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>She’s the one you dap up in the hallway like you’ve survived three wars together. Lifelong homie energy. Shoulder bump. Head nod. Mutual understanding.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>She’s also the same person who “looks out for you” by randomly bonking your head whenever you say something remotely questionable.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>That’s her love language. Mild violence.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>“Does she like you?”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>Alright. Let’s examine the evidence here.</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(95, 182, 255);\"><strong><em>• She used you as a piggyback ride for an entire week because she “didn’t feel like walking.”</em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"7p9P3CW900rdHoVk28Wx8.webp","creator":"WLM.MP4","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👩‍🦰 Female","🧑‍🎨 OC","👭 Multiple","👤 AnyPOV","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","😂 Comedy"],"chats":13890,"messages":222625,"created_at":"2026-02-23T15:38:14.740475+00:00"}